      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, having been garage-kept and frequently detailed; while you might find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use, the body lines are straight and free of any significant dings or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seats that show only light softening on the driver\u2019s bolster. All electronic features\u2014including the premium sound system, dual-zone climate control, and navigation\u2014operate exactly as they did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule with full service records available for your review. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. It is a reliable, turn-key example ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
